LEGO-Jason-NXT Version 1.0 (1 October 2010)

The main goal of the LEGO-Jason-NXT project is to implement an extension for the Jason multi-agent
system that allows one to write applications executed by the LEGO MINDSTORMS NXT robots.

Required environment variables:
JASON_HOME = Jason root directory
NXJ_HOME = NXJ root directory

Build order:

1) nxt:
cd nxt
ant jar

2) jason:
cd jason
ant jar

To upload to NXT robot:
cd nxt
ant upload

To run Jason:
cd jason
ant run

Acknowledgement: I thank associate professor Jørgen Villadsen, DTU Informatics, Denmark.

Further information and updates are available here: http://imm.dtu.dk/~jv/LEGO-Jason-NXT
